{"word":"προσφθεγκτός","slug":"προσφθεγκτός","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<el><b>προσφθεγκτός</b></el> <br/><b><a href='S:Etymology'>Etym.</a> </b>from <a href='S:προσφθέγγομαι'><el>προσφθέγγομαι</el></a>\n<p/><div class='li500'><b>I. </b><i>addressed, saluted</i>, <el>σοῦ φωνῆς</el> by thy voice, <b><a href='S:Sophocles'>Soph.</a></b><p/></div><div class='li500'><b>II. </b><a href='S:active signification'><a href='S:Active voice'>act.</a></a> <i>saluting</i>, <b><a href='S:Anthology'>Anth.</a></b><p/></div>"}]}